1da1c1abe21abdb66c8c54a4b3f61567a","tid":313312,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T09:19:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/F4a4f.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FF4a4f.gif&h=c1562504&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nHoming laser<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/F4XEs.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FF4XEs.gif&h=8633642f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nBuster飛彈<br />\n聽講即係等於光子魚雷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a22ec562aacfa458847f06d20c65993f4a9a4a4","tid":313312,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T10:14:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/F4rpD.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FF4rpD.gif&h=35e228cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nBuster Shield<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/F4hP8.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FF4hP8.gif&h=7c603f92&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n這威力......<br />\n完全係地圖炮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3f9d295b9915a278f4c54fb2fa222f554699222","tid":313312,"uid":10443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T10:23:32.000Z","msg":"個人鐘意diebuster多d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\ngunbuster前面有d悶"},{"pid":"9492dea91dc3946649603485ed5154b8e7ceb54e","tid":313312,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T10:47:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個人鐘意diebuster多d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\ngunbuster前面有d悶</blockquote><br />\n鹹魚白菜,各有所愛<br />\n不過網上的評論大部分都認為DIEBUSTER不如GUNBUSTER<br />\n不過,要續作超越原作本來就係一件好困難好罕有的事"},{"pid":"ecbf423e90e044a456870e29c79fbdd7c45f462a","tid":313312,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T10:54:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/F4KIa.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FF4KIa.gif&h=92009b86&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nDouble Buster Collider<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/F4DhI.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FF4DhI.gif&h=dc122f08&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n太陽系絕對防衛線作戰<br />\n2032年8月6日，早上4時15分，宇宙軍情報部接到情報，在天琴座3-26區發現大量宇宙怪獸，總數佔據了天空80個天文單位(AU)，約等於119.68億公里的面積。地球帝國宇宙軍需要在它們到達太陽系絕對防衛線前把它們消滅。<br />\n<br />\n過程<br />\n2032年8月8日，在帝都東京地球防衛廳的緊急對策會議上，太田中校強行闖入氣氛低迷的會議提出作戰議案:<br />\n「把廢棄的無人宇宙戰艦Exelion由Buster機組1號機與2號機（Gunbuster未合體的狀態）護送前往宇宙怪獸集結的中心，讓其亞空間引擎的縮退爐無限制地運轉而暴走。預計在2分40秒後會產生人工黑洞把宇宙怪獸消滅。而中心附近的太陽系第十三大行星雷王星也會被吞沒。」<br />\n由於第五世代型宇宙戰艦Eltreum的完成度只有16%，太田的作戰議案被接受使用。<br />\n2032年8月15日，Gunbuster由地球富士宇宙基地出發，在宇宙和Exelion會合。途中天野和美一度因太田的病情而退縮，最後在典子的鼓勵下振作。經過Gunbuster和宇宙怪獸的連番戰鬥，Exelion到達宇宙怪獸集結的中心，縮退爐無限制地運轉暴走，成功產生人工黑洞。<br />\n<br />\n結果<br />\n這次作戰計劃把99.89%的宇宙怪獸吞沒，雷王星軌道附近引起了60秒的超重力崩潰，雷王星90%物質被吞沒，魔王星、智王星偏離了原有的軌道。另一方面，重力衝擊波在六個月後到達地球，對地球產生一定程度的破壞。"},{"pid":"7aee7e37374c916e44e9dcb14552049658db2539","tid":313312,"uid":12393,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T11:09:50.000Z","msg":"出場bgm霸氣到痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0412f55ead9fdbe49426926894f1d5fe601cd0d2","tid":313312,"uid":17954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T11:15:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/F4JS2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FF4JS2.gif&h=9f85cc72&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n合體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n這是慢鏡嗎?如果合咁耐一早被敵人打爆了吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"ht